+--------+-------------+-----------+
| Name   | Description | Version   |
+--------+-------------+-----------+
| node   | Node.js     | 0.4.12    |
| node06 | Node.js     | 0.6.8     |
| node08 | Node.js     | 0.8.2     |
| ruby18 | Ruby 1.8    | 1.8.7     |
| ruby19 | Ruby 1.9    | 1.9.2p180 |
| java   | Java 6      | 1.6       |
| java7  | Java 7      | 1.7       |
+--------+-------------+-----------+

